{"tid":1829554,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【別開生面】癡肥IS領袖被捕要用卡車運走 網民：佢肯定無法逃脫","createTime":"2020-01-18T22:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T01:48:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aab604e07aa0eb724bea46b1cb298e537f137972","tid":1829554,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T22:41:44.000Z","msg":"伊拉克特種部隊周四在摩蘇爾拘捕極端組織「伊斯蘭國」（IS）其中一位重量級領導人阿尼馬（Shifa al-Nima），但由於他太肥胖，無法押上警車，最後只能坐在卡車車尾押走。<br />\n<br />\n阿尼馬體態肥胖，故被暱稱為電影《星球大戰》中的反派角色「Jabba the Hutt」。當他被捕的照片上傳後，引起網民熱議，紛紛上載「Jabba the Hutt」的照片嘲笑，「有一點可以肯定，他沒有機會逃走」、「Jabba the Hutt（阿尼馬）真的不修篇幅」。<br />\n<br />\n阿尼馬據稱體重達136公斤（300磅），他在摩蘇爾的藏身處被拘捕，被拍到安置在一輛卡車車尾被押走。伊拉克警方表示，阿尼馬是IS的重量級領導人之一，他涉嫌2014年IS佔據摩蘇爾後，下令破壞市內先知尤努斯（Prophet Yunus）的墳墓。<br />\n<br />\n除了摧毁古墓外，阿尼馬又被指專門負責下令處決拒絕效忠的IS學者和牧師，並煽動民眾反對安全部隊。一位在敘利亞與IS作戰的英國人吉福德（Macer Gifford）發推文，寫道：「（他）負責處決男人、女人和兒童，這個禽獸是強姦犯及殺人犯」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200118/large/1579334108_4eca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200118%2Flarge%2F1579334108_4eca.jpg&h=5baccef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200118/DWZ52STDWBJQX3SEDTJEVKLGOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200118%2FDWZ52STDWBJQX3SEDTJEVKLGOI%2F&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1ILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=75a58246\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200118%2FDWZ52STDWBJQX3SEDTJEVKLGOI%2F&h=9c386d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200118/DWZ52STDWBJQX3SEDTJEVKLGOI/</a>"},{"pid":"aa1b06c22388e6733691ca7f3e7f3809c67124ca","tid":1829554,"uid":183587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T22:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b90de1c14709507b98bb89dc8